            "choices":[
                "Jake.",
                "Alex.",
                "Other."
            ],
            "content":"<div class=\"\"><div> <span>By: Gainer<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJake: A green scaled, 20 year old T-rex about 6ft 8in tall and weighs about 200 pounds. Jake enjoys many things, normally going with the flow, but he really loves the feeling of getting bigger. To Jake, there is no better feeling than adding an extra pound of weight to your frame be it muscle or fat.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlex: A darker scaled, 19 year old T-rex about 7ft 4in tall and weighs about 240 pounds. Alex is competitive, vowing to beat anybody in any challenge he's asked. Alex would win a strong man challenge one day and an eating contest the next, there are no limits to his spirit.</span></div></div>",
