    "info":{
        "author_id":"thomasfan99",
        "author_name":"AWVR1206",
        "brief_description":"Dinosaurs grow bigger!",
        "created":1587828120,
        "description":"<td align=\"left\" class=\"norm\">In this story, dinosaurs will get rounder.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThere will be two types of dinosaurs:<br>\r\n   Feral (back before they went extinct)<br>\r\n   Anthro (modern times where they are able to walk like people and wear clothes)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThey will grow via:<br>\r\nWeight gain (keep it gradual)<br>\r\nInflation (air, water, blueberry, etc)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThey can be different ages, ranging from 13 to 25. You are free to create/include your own dinosaur characters; be sure to include whether they are feral or anthro, their personalities and their age. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNo vore<br>\r\nNo gore<br>\r\nNo death<br>\r\nNo cursing<br>\r\nNo sexual content (ex. no having sex, no sticking hoses up private parts, etc.)<br>\r\nNo nudity<br>\r\nNo diapers<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAny chapters that violate these rules will be deleted.</td>",
